Sentencas: The paper investigates the influence of the La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-d-Gd0.1Ce0.9O1.95 (LSC-GDC) composite cathode interlayer on the operation of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: Magnetron sputtered LSC-GDC composite cathode interlayer for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thin composite layers with the different GDC content are obtained by the reactive magnetron sputtering.
Titulo: Magnetron sputtered LSC-GDC composite cathode interlayer for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The impact of the high-temperature annealing on the LSC-GDC phase composition is studied by the X-ray diffraction instrument using additionally a synchro-tron radiation.
Titulo: Magnetron sputtered LSC-GDC composite cathode interlayer for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The NiO-YSZ anodes with the YSZ electrolyte thin film and GDC barrier layer are used for the SOFC fabrication.
Titulo: Magnetron sputtered LSC-GDC composite cathode interlayer for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The current-voltage curves and impedance spectra of SOFCs are obtained in the temperature range of 700-800 degrees C.
Titulo: Magnetron sputtered LSC-GDC composite cathode interlayer for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is shown that not annealed composite layers with-50 vol% GDC content possess the most efficient electrochemical activity.
Titulo: Magnetron sputtered LSC-GDC composite cathode interlayer for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density of the SOFC with the LSC-GDC interlayer is 1322, 1041 and 796 mW/cm2 at 800, 750 and 700 degrees C, respectively, which is 20-35% higher than that of the cell without cathode interlayer.(c) 2022
